<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Release Notes</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Release Notes">
      <subsection name="2.0.0 (unreleased)">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: TBD</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Base the skin on Maven Fluido Skin version 1.6, used to be 1.4. Much better on mobile!</li>
          <li>Modify the "Fork me on GitHub" ribbon support, defaulting to right top green ribbon, configurable in site.xml
              by element <tt>&lt;custom&gt;&lt;hippoSkin&gt;&lt;gitHub&gt;&lt;projectId&gt;</tt>.</li>
          <li>Various styling improvements.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.04.00">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: Sept 06, 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1247">HIPPLUG-1247</a><br/>
            Typography may look more close to Fluido.
          </li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1354">HIPPLUG-1354</a><br/>
            Change scheme of links to https.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.03.00">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: Jan 14, 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1242">HIPPLUG-1242</a><br/>
            Line numbers failing when generated on non-Windows env.
          </li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1243">HIPPLUG-1243</a><br/>
            Integrate with SyntaxHighlighter for source code generation.
          </li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1244">HIPPLUG-1244</a><br/>
            Make (sub)section headers font bigger or more recognizable.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.02">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: Sep 29, 2014</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-929">HIPPLUG-929</a><br/>
            Render sub menu items again (broken in 1.02.01 only).
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.01">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: Aug 27, 2014</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-819">HIPPLUG-819</a><br/>
            Line numbers fixed when using maven-site-plugin 3.3.</li>
          <li> <a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-904">HIPPLUG-904</a><br/>
            Various changes: some styling, fix Google search, removed double menu item selection for the index.html.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.00">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: April 4, 2014</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Changed Hippo Campus link text to Onehippo.org.</li>
          <li>Smallinfo class style improvements.</li>
          <li>By default, not applying a date format, will show the date as "dd Month YYYY".</li>
          <li>By default set sourceLineNumbersEnabled style to true, if it is not set already.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.01.01">
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed logo path (was wrong with nested paths).</li>
          <li>Replace icons for external links.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.01.00">
        <ul>
          <li>Engage!</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
